prompts.frontCover: Flat 2D minimalist vector illustration of a birthday greeting card. In the center, cartoon versions of Lao Lao (person on the left in the photo) and Jordan (person on the right in the photo) are depicted in a humorous beach scene. Lao Lao is comically trying to drag a giant, oversized inflatable crab along the sand, pulling it by one of its large claws. She has a determined, funny expression. Jordan is standing behind her, laughing and holding a tiny, comically small beach pail and shovel, looking completely unhelpful but amused. They are both wearing the outfits from the photo (Lao Lao in a light blue sweatshirt and black pants, Jordan in a tan hoodie and dark pants, with any logos removed). The scene is minimalist, with a simple wavy line for the ocean in the background and a few stylized clouds in the sky. The color palette is soft pastels with pops of bright color for the crab and pail. Centered above the couple is the text "Happy Birthday Lao Lao!" in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script. The overall composition is clean, playful, and centered on a plain off-white background.
